00:27:32.384 --> 00:27:34.319
Oh, elle est là. Je te rappelle.

00:27:37.781 --> 00:27:38.865
Tu es de retour.

00:27:44.104 --> 00:27:45.247
Attendez.

00:27:46.690 --> 00:27:48.690
