00:40:48.596 --> 00:40:50.823
- Hé !
- Salut, Seol-ha.

00:40:51.366 --> 00:40:52.576
Voici Min-gi.

00:40:53.159 --> 00:40:55.620
Joyeux anniversaire aujourd'hui.

00:40:56.396 --> 00:40:58.748
Promets-moi que nous serons amoureux

00:40:59.107 --> 00:41:00.125
